{"tid":1296922,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"講真，達哥有乜事的話，你良心過唔過意得去？","createTime":"2019-07-08T13:37:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T06:42:01.000Z","uid":58335,"like":18,"dislike":201,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"7b70fcd25b6f3a5bb476b6ac599a5cab15aa2d17","tid":1296922,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:37:17.000Z","msg":"連衛兵有無想過你呢種一時之快會對當事人有幾大傷害？傳左出去人地點見人，張相仲要咁清？你地班友可能就睇得好happy，人地分分鐘就躲係屋企喊。人有時好脆弱，達哥有乜事的話，你良心過唔過意得去？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我勸你放出黎之前三思一下，唔好受班花生友影響，呢度D人有野睇就唔會理他人感受，當中仲有成班小朋友字都未識得幾個，希望你可以作出獨立判斷，唔好助長網絡暴力，做埋晒D損人不利己的事。"},{"pid":"a9ca3c820dd780265bb93bfab675c2b9fb2411f1","tid":1296922,"uid":58335,"like":6,"dislike":32,"score":-26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:37:46.000Z","msg":"利申：達哥6年fans"},{"pid":"d11ed2de8ef7dc7ec1383a5ccc9b33ca63c43789","tid":1296922,"uid":58335,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T14:05:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b2dd2e471c9abcd8b76460f2bc37c2145550d10","tid":1296922,"uid":205928,"like":29,"dislike":2,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T14:13:59.000Z","msg":"冇人想理假膠po"},{"pid":"4645382d693c6f3c5b0e11fefdb99716484ca4c1","tid":1296922,"uid":58335,"like":4,"dislike":17,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"0b2dd2e471c9abcd8b76460f2bc37c2145550d10","tid":1296922,"uid":205928,"like":29,"dislike":2,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T14:13:59.000Z","msg":"冇人想理假膠po"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T14:19:16.000Z","msg":"認真架<br />\n唔想連衛兵日日批鬥達哥"},{"pid":"b1030d44e0ce750faca7846aa1ed5609205fde45","tid":1296922,"uid":58335,"like":2,"dislike":23,"score":-21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T15:24:11.000Z","msg":"邊條連衛兵比負評???<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad51adfd7f21b5af7b866792517f6a0dea8f1980","tid":1296922,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"0b2dd2e